LIE - Flashcards app
====================

Installing requirements

1)For Debian-based SO:

    sudo apt-get install python-setuptools python-pygame python-opengl \
  python-gst0.10 python-enchant gstreamer0.10-plugins-good python-dev \
  build-essential libgl1-mesa-dev-lts-quantal libgles2-mesa-dev-lts-quantal\
  python-pip

2)Download Cython from:
    
    http://cython.org/release/Cython-0.20.2.tar.gz

  Extract and run:
    
    sudo python setup.py install

3)Download and install Kivy:

    git clone git://github.com/kivy/kivy.git
  
  In the kivy directory run:

    sudo python setup.py install
  
